&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute comprehensive sales and partnership strategies to drive revenue growth and ecosystem expansion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and pursue new business opportunities, strategic alliances, and partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and manage a team of partnership managers and sales professionals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and execute a long-term vision for sales and partnerships to ensure sustainable growth and alignment with Scroll’s strategic objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partnership and Revenue Development:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate and enhance relationships with key partners, including dApps, liquidity providers, and other stakeholders in the Web3 ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the integration and onboarding of new partners, collaborating with the International Markets team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Scroll at industry events and conferences to build and maintain a robust network.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market Analysis and Strategy Execution:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze market trends, competitor activities, and customer feedback to identify growth opportunities and areas for improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with product, marketing, and development teams to ensure alignment of sales strategies with product offerings and market needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop sales materials, presentations, and other collateral to support business development efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Management:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set and monitor key performance indicators (KPIs) for the sales and partnerships team. TVL, volume and projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and prioritize a diverse portfolio of projects and partnerships, ensuring alignment with Scroll’s vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide regular reports and updates to the executive team on sales performance, market trends, and strategic initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in a senior sales or partnerships role within the blockchain, DeFi, or technology sectors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent leadership and team management skills, with the ability to inspire and motivate a remote team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication and negotiation skills, with the ability to articulate complex issues clearly and persuasively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to analyze and interpret market data, trading performance, and emerging trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel for community events and business meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
