&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Cultivate and enhance partnerships with decentralized applications (dApps) and liquidity providers, leveraging expertise in key account management to foster collaborations within Scroll and its partners’ ecosystems for Turkiye market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Play an instrumental role in shaping and executing the strategy for resource distribution within the Scroll network.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Analyze the evolving landscape of dApps to identify emerging trends and opportunities that can augment the Scroll ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
