&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Deep knowledge and a strong network in the Turkish Web3 ecosystem, including CEXs, builders, entrepreneurs, university blockchain clubs, and opinion leaders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Deep understanding of and integration within the Ethereum and L2 community&lt;/li&gt;
